    # Convert linear index to multi-dimensional index
    # For the split dimension, we use the output dimension size
    # For other dimensions, we use the input dimension sizes

    # Linear index = pre_idx * dim_size_input * post_dim + split_idx * post_dim + post_idx
    # But we need to map to the correct position in the input tensor

